"{\"uid\": \"scrippsnews.com-sports-paris-2024-olympics-imane-khelif-algerian-boxer-who-had-gender-test-issue-wins-first-olympic-fight-when-opponent-quits\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Imane Khelif of Algeria won her opening Olympic boxing bout on Thursday when opponent Angela Carini of Italy quit after just 46 seconds.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 16, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999991861385426, \"rank\": 8.130005134236599e-07, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 86, \"end\": 99, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 103, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9846507093122249, \"rank\": 0.015564929402595217, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif was disqualified from the 2023 world championships after failing an unspecified gender eligibility test, and her presence at theParis Olympicshas become a divisive issue.\", \"from\": 138, \"to\": 315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini and Khelif exchanged only a few punches before Carini walked away and abandoned the bout, an extremely unusual occurrence in Olympic boxing.\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9996246428496567, \"rank\": 0.0003754980963160258, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 371, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9996246428496567, \"rank\": 0.0003754980963160258, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini, whose headgear apparently became dislodged at least once before she quit, did not shake Khelif's hand after the decision was announced, but she cried in the ring on her knees.\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 465, \"end\": 471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9996246428496567, \"rank\": 0.0003754980963160258, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterward, a still-tearful Carini said she quit because of intense pain in her nose after the opening punches.\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9996246428496567, \"rank\": 0.0003754980963160258, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini, who had a spot of blood on her trunks, said she wasn't making a political statement and was not refusing to fight Khelif.\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 761, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9996246428496567, \"rank\": 0.0003754980963160258, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt a severe pain in my nose, and with the maturity of a boxer, I said 'enough,' because I did not want to, I did not want to, I could not finish the match,\\\" Carini said.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1054, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9996246428496567, \"rank\": 0.0003754980963160258, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini further said she is not qualified to decide whether Khelif should be allowed to compete.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9996246428496567, \"rank\": 0.0003754980963160258, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED STORY |US tennis sensation Coco Gauff upset at Olympics  \\\"I am not here to judge or pass judgment,\\\" Carini said.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.999999064324112, \"rank\": 9.332675745453661e-07, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}, {\"begin\": 1273, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9996246428496567, \"rank\": 0.0003754980963160258, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If an athlete is this way, and in that sense it's not right or it is right, it's not up to me to decide.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just did my job as a boxer.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I got into the ring and fought.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did it with my head held high and with a broken heart for not having finished the last kilometer.\\\"\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif is an accomplished amateur who won a silver medal at the International Boxing Association's 2022 world championships.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1620, \"end\": 1652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0195726072044904e-35, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IBA - which has been banned from the Olympics since 2019 after years of disputes with the IOC - disqualified her from last year's championships shortly before her gold-medal match because of what it claimed were elevated levels of testosterone.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1685, \"end\": 1688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9049110622725959, \"rank\": 0.10508096951155597, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1775, \"end\": 1778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.049305358199587e-47, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old entered the ring at the North Paris Arena to a chorus of cheers, but the crowd was confused by the bout's sudden end.\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1977, \"end\": 1982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.661999802666164e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Italy coach Emanuele Renzini said he discussed the matchup with Carini and offered to allow her to back out earlier, but the boxer had been \\\"very determined\\\" to fight until the opening minute.\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2065, \"end\": 2070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9846507093122249, \"rank\": 0.015564929402595217, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2129, \"end\": 2135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9996246428496567, \"rank\": 0.0003754980963160258, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am heartbroken because I am a fighter,\\\" Carini said.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2314, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2302, \"end\": 2308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9996246428496567, \"rank\": 0.0003754980963160258, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My father taught me to be a warrior.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have always stepped into the ring with honor and I have always (served) my country with loyalty.\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And this time I could not do it because I could not fight anymore, and so I ended the match.\\\"\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif could clinch an Olympic medal with a victory in her quarterfinal bout on Saturday against Anna Luca Hamori, Hungary's first Olympic boxer.\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2644, \"end\": 2648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"score\": 0.9998997766179087, \"rank\": 8.236696933896226e-05, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\"}, {\"begin\": 2662, \"end\": 2669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7415879440543608, \"rank\": 0.34845715284551165, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hamori expressed no concern about fighting Khelif.\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not scared,\\\" said Hamori, who trounced Marissa Williamson Pohlman of Australia.\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2791, \"end\": 2798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marissa_Cooper\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.3652792465702876e-17, \"text\": \"Marissa\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marissa_Cooper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marissa_Cooper\"}, {\"begin\": 2799, \"end\": 2809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zion_Williamson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.375410467748102e-19, \"text\": \"Williamson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zion_Williamson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zion_Williamson\"}, {\"begin\": 2821, \"end\": 2830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.988270353185881, \"rank\": 0.009235154851663764, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not care about the press story and social media.\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If she or he is a man, it will be a bigger victory for me if I win.\\\"\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's passport says she is female.\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 2994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hamori and Khelif have never sparred, but they have competed in the same tournament before.\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hamori repeatedly said she is not paying attention to the controversy because it's only a hindrance to her quest for gold.\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am trying to not use my phone before the fight,\\\" Hamori said.\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3276, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want to care about the comments or the story or the news.\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just want to stay focused on myself.\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did it before my last two fights, so I think this is the key, and we will see.\\\"\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Hamori could only shrug at Carini's decision to quit.\", \"from\": 3467, \"to\": 3524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3498, \"end\": 3504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9996246428496567, \"rank\": 0.0003754980963160258, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was her choice,\\\" Hamori said.\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not understand, because I thought every boxer's mind is the same like mine, to never give up.\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was her choice.\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3682, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not know what was the reason.\", \"from\": 3683, \"to\": 3718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's her life, but I know I want to do this in my own life.\\\"\", \"from\": 3719, \"to\": 3779, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After years of competition in amateur tournaments around the world, Khelif and Lin Yu\\u2011ting of Taiwan suddenly have received massive scrutiny for their presence in Paris.\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3875, \"end\": 3881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999996462543721, \"rank\": 2.2870111776631074e-07, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 3944, \"end\": 3949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.661999802666164e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin won IBA world championships in 2018 and 2022, but the governing body stripped her of a bronze medal last year because it claimed she failed to meet unspecified eligibility requirements in a biochemical test.\", \"from\": 3951, \"to\": 4162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin begins her Paris run Friday.\", \"from\": 4164, \"to\": 4196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4179, \"end\": 4184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.661999802666164e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She fights Sitora Turdibekova of Uzbekistan in her opening bout after receiving a first-round bye as the No.\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4230, \"end\": 4240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1375638354694866e-13, \"text\": \"Uzbekistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1 seed in the 57-kilogram category, although Olympic seeding is frequently unindicative of the top medal contenders in a division.\", \"from\": 4306, \"to\": 4436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Algerian Olympic Committee issued a statement Wednesday condemning what it termed \\\"lies\\\" and \\\"unethical targeting and maligning of our esteemed athlete, Imane Khelif, with baseless propaganda from certain foreign media outlets.\\\"\", \"from\": 4438, \"to\": 4670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4442, \"end\": 4468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algerian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Algerian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algerian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algerian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4595, \"end\": 4607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Italian Premier Giorgia Meloni, who was visiting Italy athletes in the Olympic Village on Thursday, voiced criticism that Carini had to box Khelif, saying she had since 2021 opposed allowing athletes with \\\"genetically male\\\" characteristics to compete against women.\", \"from\": 4672, \"to\": 4937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4672, \"end\": 4679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9914285422074302, \"rank\": 0.007721328086645152, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 4688, \"end\": 4702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Meloni\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giorgia Meloni\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Meloni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Meloni\"}, {\"begin\": 4721, \"end\": 4726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9846507093122249, \"rank\": 0.015564929402595217, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4743, \"end\": 4758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1608618067050024e-20, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 4794, \"end\": 4800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9996246428496567, \"rank\": 0.0003754980963160258, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED STORY |Djokovic outlasts Nadal, overcoming major hurdle in quest for first Olympic gold  \\\"We have to pay attention, in an attempt to not discriminate, that we are actually discriminating\\\" against women's rights, Meloni said.\", \"from\": 4939, \"to\": 5171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4972, \"end\": 4977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999899496288, \"rank\": 1.0050340084534156e-08, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said it was necessary to guarantee the rights of athletes so they are competing on an even playing field.\", \"from\": 5173, \"to\": 5282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In these things what counts is your dedication, your head and character, but it also counts having a parity of arms,\\\" Meloni said.\", \"from\": 5284, \"to\": 5415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif and Lin are two-time Olympians who fought in the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 5417, \"to\": 5485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin has been an elite-level amateur boxer for a decade and Khelif for six years.\", \"from\": 5486, \"to\": 5566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC repeatedly defended the boxers' right to compete this week.\", \"from\": 5568, \"to\": 5635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5572, \"end\": 5575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.049305358199587e-47, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic boxing reached gender parity for the first time this year, with 124 men and 124 women competing in Paris.\", \"from\": 5636, \"to\": 5749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5743, \"end\": 5748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.661999802666164e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC said it made its eligibility decisions on boxers based on the gender-related rules that applied at the 2016 Rio de Janeiro Olympics.\", \"from\": 5751, \"to\": 5891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5755, \"end\": 5758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.049305358199587e-47, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several sports have updated their gender rules over the past three years, including World Aquatics, World Athletics and the International Cycling Union.\", \"from\": 5892, \"to\": 6044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5992, \"end\": 6007, \"title\": \"http: